                    <span>This book is REALLY for coursework : someone who is going to sit down and read and work thru this book sequentially, not randomly like a reference book.<br>Other than that caveat it does what it promises ably but be aware that it is MATHS heavy and REQUIRES the programme work.</span>
                  
